column2: {@st59b} Adventure Journal {nl}{@st59s}- Your game progress is recorded in the Adventure Journal. {nl} - You can progress your Adventure Index through contents such as: obtaining items, hunting monsters, crafting and map exploration.{nl}    Adventure Index : The total of all your indexes. {nl}    Growth : 5 points per character level and class level {nl}    Items : Equipment : grade X 10 points, Books : 10 points, Others : 1 point {nl}    Monsters : 10 points per monster (50 points for Boss Monsters) {nl}    Maps : 1 point per 10% explored {nl}    Quests : 1 point per quest {nl}    Achievements : Varies by achievement {nl}    Crafting : 10 points {nl}    Collection : 5 points for a deck and 45 points when it is completed {nl} - You can receive special rewards from an NPC in town depending on your Adventure Index. {/}
column3: {@st59b}모험일지{nl}{@st59s} - 자신의 진행한 정보가 모험일지에 기록{nl} - 아이템 습득, 몬스터 사냥, 제작, 맵탐험, 콘텐츠 진행으로 모험지수 획득{nl}    모험지수 : 다른 모든 지수의 총 합{nl}    성장 : 레벨 및 직업 레벨당 5점{nl}    아이템 : 장비 : 등급 X 10점, 책 : 10점, 기타 : 1점{nl}    몬스터 : 몬스터당 10점 (보스 : 50점){nl}    지역탐색 : 10%당 1점{nl}    퀘스트 : 퀘스트당 1점{nl}    업적 : 업적별로 다름{nl}    제작법 : 개당 10점{nl}    콜렉션 : 덱 5점 , 완성 45점{nl} - 획득한 모험지수에 따라 마을 NPC에게서 보상 획득{/}
column4: {@st59b}Adventure Journal {nl} {@st59s} - Adventurer journal mencatat pencapaian dalam petualangan {nl} - Item yang didapat, Monster, Crafting, Map, Content, Achievement

column2: {@st59b}Quests{nl}{@st59s} - When you are on a new quest, it will be added to the quest tracker. {nl} - A main quest is displayed in yellow color, while a subquest is displayed in blue. {nl} - The arrow on the character's foot leads to the location of your quest. {nl} - If you completed a quest, a 'Return' icon is displayed on the quest tracker. {nl}    (Teleports you to the Quest NPC using the Backspace key or a mouse-click) {nl} - Add or remove quests in the quest tracker by ticking or unticking the box in front of the quest name. {/}

column2: {@st59b}Classes{nl}{@st59s}- You can learn new skills by growing the Circle of your class. {nl} - You can choose from 3 available classes to advance to from your 1st to 2nd advancement. {nl} - You can advance to the same class up to 3 times. {nl} - You cannot change back to your previous class once you advanced to another class. {nl} - You have to consume all your Skill Points to be able to advance. {nl} - You can choose the same class.{nl}{@st59b}Skills{nl}{@st59s} - You can increase the rank of each skill up to level 5.{nl} - Attributes learned from your Masters can be seen below your skills. {/}

column2: When you report a bug, your gameplay up to that point will be sent to our server.{nl}The replay file will be of much help in resolving the bug. Do you want to send it?
column3: 버그를 제보하시면 현재까지 게임플레이 화면이 서버로 전송됩니다. 전송된 리플레이 파일은 버그 수정에 큰 도움이 됩니다. 전송하시겠습니까?
column4: Jika kamu menemukan error atau bug dalam game segera laporkan!! Laporan perihal bug/error akan sangat membantu. Ingin melaporkan?

column2: {@st41b}Entering a description is not mandatory, but it will help us a lot in analyzing the bug.
column3: {@st41b}버그 내용은 필수 입력 사항이 아니지만 분석에 도움이 됩니다.
column4: {@st41b}Detail Bug adalah bagian yang harus di isi agar analisa jelas.

column2: {@st59b}Equipment {nl}{@st59s} - Hair/Costume: Equipment to change a characters appearance. {nl} - Weapon: One-handed or two-handed weapons {nl} (sub-weapon/shield can be equipped with one-handed weapon) {nl} - Armor: Top, Bottom, Gloves, Shoes. {nl} - Accessories: 1 Necklace and 2 Bracelets. {nl} {/}
column3: {@st59b}착용장비{nl}{@st59s} - 헤어/코스튬 : 외형 변경 가능 아이템 착용{nl} - 무기 : 한손 장비 및 양손 장비 착용 가능{nl}   (한손 장비 착용시 서브웨폰/방패 착용 가능 ){nl} - 방어구 : 상의, 하의, 장갑, 신발 착용{nl} - 악세서리 : 목걸이 1개, 팔찌 2개 착용{nl}   (팔찌2는 Alt키로 비교해 보기/장착 가능){/}
column4: {@st59b}Equipments {nl}{@st59s} - Hair/Costume : Mengganti tampilan character {nl} - Weapon : Senjata One-hand atau two-hand {nl}  (sub-weapon/shield dapat digunakan dengan one-hand weapon) {nl} - Armor : Top, Pants, Gloves, Shoes {nl} - Accessories : 1 Necklace dan 2 Bracelets {nl} {/}

column4: Jika kamu berhasil mencari anggota party sesuai syarat, {nl}[Party Ditemukan!] Notice akan muncul.{nl}Kamu juga akan direkomendasikan ke party lain.

column2: {@st59b}Gem/Card Enhancement{nl}{@st59s} - Select a gem or card from your inventory to enhance it.{nl} - All items with exception of quest items can be used as materials for enhancing gems.{nl} (Most effective when using a gem as material){nl} - Cards can only be enhanced by using other cards.{/}
column3: {@st59b}젬/카드 강화{nl}{@st59s} - 강화할 젬 또는 카드를 인벤토리에서 선택하여 등록{nl} - 퀘스트 아이템을 제외한 모든 아이템을 젬 강화 재료로 사용 가능{nl}   (젬을 재료로 사용했을 때 효율이 가장 높음){nl} - 카드 강화는 다른 카드들로만 재료로 사용 가능{/}
column4: {@st59b}Gem/Card Enhancement{nl}{@st59s} - Pilih Gem atau Card untuk di enhance dari inventory{nl} - Semua item kecuali quest items dapat digunakan sebagai materials{nl} (Yang paling efektif adalah Gem sebagai material){nl} - Card hanya bisa di enhanced dengan menggunakan card lain{/}

column2: {@st59b}Quests{nl}{@st59s} - When you are on a new quest, it will be added to the quests window.{nl} - A main quest is displayed in yellow color, while a subquest is displayed in blue.{nl} - The arrow on your character's foot leads to the location of your quest{nl} - A 'Return' icon is displayed in the quests window when a quest is completed{nl}  (Teleports you to the Quest NPC using the Backspace key or a mouse-click){nl} - Add or remove quests in the quests window by ticking or unticking the box in front of the quest name{/}
column3: {@st59b}퀘스트{nl}{@st59s} - 퀘스트 획득시 퀘스트 지령창에 등록{nl} - 메인퀘스트는 노란색, 서브퀘스트는 파란색 표시{nl} - 캐릭터 발 밑의 화살표로 퀘스트 위치를 표시{nl} - 퀘스트 완료시 퀘스트 지령창에 돌아가기 아이콘 표시{nl}  (백스페이스나 마우스 클릭으로 완료 NPC로 순간이동){nl} - 퀘스트 지령창에 등록/해제시 퀘스트 이름 앞 체크 선택{/}
column4: {@St59b}Quest{nl}{@st59s} - Ketika kamu berada di quest baru, itu akan ditambahkan ke jendela quest {nl} -. Sebuah main quest ditampilkan dalam warna kuning, sementara subquest ditampilkan dalam warna biru . {nl} - Panah pada kaki karakter Kamu mengarah ke lokasi quest kamu. {nl} - ikon 'Kembali' ditampilkan di jendela quest ketika quest selesai {nl} (teleport Kamu ke Quest NPC menggunakan tombol backspace atau mouse-klik) {nl} - Menambahkan atau menghapus quest di jendela quest dengan mencentang atau tidak kotak di depan nama quest {/}

column3: {@st59b}상점{nl}{@st59s} - 아이템을 여러 개 판매/구매하려면 Shift + 우클릭 후 개수 입력{nl} - 아이템을 전량 판매하려면 마우스 더블 우클릭으로 이용{/}
column4: {@st59b}Shop{nl}{@st59s} - Gunakan Shift + klik-Kanan untuk memasukkan jumlah untuk menjual/membeli beberapa item{nl} - Klik-Kanan dua kali untuk menjual semua item{/}

This item will disappear from your inventory{nl}Resets your all Skill Points.
column3: 사용한 아이템은 인벤토리에서 사라지며{nl}전체 스킬 포인트가 초기화 됩니다.{/}
column4: Item yang telah digunakan akan menghilang dari inventory. {nl}Reset semua skill point kamu.

column2: {@st59b}Classes{nl}{@st59s}- You can learn new skills by growing the Circle of your class. {nl} - You can choose from 3 available classes to advance to from your 1st to 2nd advancement. {nl} - You can advance to the same class up to 3 times. {nl} - You cannot change back to your previous class once you advanced to another class. {nl} - You have to consume all your Skill Points to be able to advance. {nl} - You can choose the same class.{nl}{@st59b}Skills{nl}{@st59s} - You can increase the rank of each skill up to level 5.{nl} - Attributes learned from your Masters can be seen below your skills. {/}
column3: {@st59b}클래스{nl}{@st59s} - 클래스의 서클을 성장시켜 해당 클래스의 스킬을 습득{nl} - 1차 직업에서 2차 직업로 전직할 경우 3개 클래스 선택 가능{nl} - 동일한 직업으로 총 3회까지 전직 가능{nl} - 동일한 클래스도 선택 가능{nl}{@st59b}스킬{nl}{@st59s} - 각 랭크별 스킬은 최대 5레벨 증가 가능{nl} - 마스터에게 배운 특성은 스킬 하단에서 확인 가능{/}
column4: {@st59b}Class{nl}{@st59s} - Kamu dapat belajar skill baru dengan meningkatnya Circle class kamu. {nl} - Kamu dapat memilih dari 3 class yang tersedia ke advance dari 1st ke 2nd advancement. {nl} - Kamu dapat advance class yang sama 3 kali. {nl} - Kamu tidak dapat kembali ke class sebelumnya setelah kamu advanced ke class lain. {nl} - Kamu harus menggunakan semua Skill Point agar bisa advance. {nl} - Kamu dapat memilih class yang sama.{nl}{@st59b}Skill{nl}{@st59s} - Kamu dapat meningkatkan rank setiap skill sampai level 5.{nl} - Attribute dipelajari dari Master kamu dapat dilihat di bawah skill kamu. {/}

column2: {@st59s}A mining town that has progressed thanks to the Crystal Mine.{nl}This city received minor damage during Medzio Diena.{/}
column3: {@st59s}수정광산을 중심으로 발전한 광업도시,{nl}신수의 날에 가장 경미한 피해를 입었다.{/}
column4: {@st59s}Sebuah kota pertambangan yang telah maju karena Tambang Kristal. {Nl} Kota ini menerima kerusakan kecil saat Medzio Diena.{/}

column2: {@st59s}We tried to protect ourselves by relying on the giant castle during Medzio Diena.{nl}But the horrifying disaster even swallowed the castle.{/}
column3: {@st59s}신수의 날에 거대한 성곽에 의지해 재앙을 막아보려 했지만,{nl}재앙은 그 성곽마저도 삼켜버렸다.{/}
column4: {@st59s}Kami mencoba untuk berlindung dari bencana dengan mengandalkan benteng raksasa saat Medzio Diena. {nl}Bencana mengerikan bahkan menghancurkan seluruh kota.{/}

column2: You can store only tradable items, but at the cost of 1 Potential.{nl}Withdrawing from Team Storage will deduct your remaining{nl}trades by 1 regardless of the number of items you take out.
column3: 거래가 가능한 아이템만 보관할 수 있으며, 포텐셜 1이 감소합니다.{nl}팀 창고에서 아이템을 꺼낼 때는 아이템 갯수에 관계없이 거래 가능횟수가 1 차감됩니다.
column4: Kamu dapat menyimpan tradable item tapi dengan biaya 1 Potential.{nl}Menarik dari Team Storage akan mengurangi trade tersisa 1 terlepas dari jumlah item yang kamu ambil.

column2: * The guild master can send items to guild members.{nl}* Items can be collected through the Message Box.
column3: * 이 아이템은 길드 마스터가 길드원에게 양도할 수 있고, 그 아이템은{nl}수령한 길드원에게 귀속됩니다.{nl}* 아이템은 메시지함에서 수령할 수 있습니다.
column4: * Guild Master dapat mengirim item ke guild member.{nl}* Item dapat dikumpulkan melalui Message Box.

column2: {@st59b}Instanced Dungeons{nl}{@st59s}Content where your group has to achieve certain objectives in independent instanced zones.{nl}You can either create a party before entering or automatically search for a party to challenge a dungeon.{nl} - Dungeons : Enter by talking to the dungeon entrance NPC in each respective level zone.{nl} - Missions : Enter by talking to the Mercenary Post Receptionists in Fedimian.{nl} - Saalus Convent Mission : Enter by talking to Sister Lhasa at Saalus Convent.{nl}{/}
column3: {@st59b}인스턴스 던전{nl}{@st59s}독립된 인스턴스 존에서 목표 달성을 위해 파티 단위로 진행하는 콘텐츠입니다.{nl}입장 전에 파티를 구성해 도전하거나 자동으로 파티를 찾아 도전할 수 있습니다.{nl} - 던전 : 각 레벨 대의 존에서 던전 입장  NPC를 통해 입장{nl} - 의뢰소 미션 : 페디미안 용병 의뢰소 접수원을 통해 입장{nl} - 살러스 수녀원 미션 : 살러스 수녀원에서 수녀 라사를 통해 입장{nl}{/}
column4: {@st59b}Instanced Dungeon{nl}{@st59s}Konten dimana grup kamu memiliki tujuan tertentu di independent instanced zone.{nl}Kamu juga dapat membuat party sebelum masuk atau otomatis mencari  sebuah party untuk menantang dungeon.{nl} - Dungeon : Masuk dengan bicara ke dungeon entrance NPC pada setiap level zone.{nl} - Mission : Masuk dengan bicara ke Mercenary Post Receptionist di Fedimian.{nl} - Saalus Convent Mission : Masuk dengan bicara ke  Sister Lhasa at Saalus Convent.{nl}{/}

column2: This item will disappear from your inventory{nl}and all %s will be reset.{/}
column3: 사용한 아이템은 인벤토리에서 사라지며{nl}전체 %s가 초기화 됩니다.{/}
column4: Item yang digunakan menghilang dari inventory kamu{nl}dan semua %s akan direset.{/}

column2: The remaining time can be seen in Character Settings.{/}
column3: 캐릭터 정보창에서 잔여시간을 확인하실 수 있습니다.{/}
column4: Sisa waktu dapat dilihat pada Character Setting.{/}

column2: Temple Shooter is gathering the Vubbes back to the Crystal Mine that is now void of Mirtis' rule.{nl}Defeat Temple Shooter and help make Crystal Mine safe once more.
column3: 미르티스 지배가 사라진 수정광산에 템플슈터가 부베들을 다시 불러들이고 있습니다.{nl}템플슈터를 처치하고 수정광산이 다시 안전해지도록 도와주세요.
column4: Temple Shooter mengumpulkan Vubbe kembali ke Crystal Mine yang sekarang kosong dari aturan Mirtis.{nl}Kalahkan Temple Shooter dan bantu membuat Crystal Mine aman sekali lagi.

column4: Hanya pengguna Token yang bisa mengakses Team Storage. Tradable item dapat disimpan disini.
